{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ABOUT THE GAME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">TV Beast is a first-person survival horror game viewed through a body-cam perspective. You play as a maintenance worker called to repair issues at a remote estate. But upon arrival, you discover a terrifying monster with a TV for a head is on the loose. This creature can manifest a range of horrifying entities and hazards. Armed with a unique remote control, you\u2019ll have to confront and outsmart the TV Beast to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Body-Cam Perspective</u></h2></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The main character's actions are seen through a body-cam, creating a unique first-person view. This body-cam effect, combined with realistic lighting, gives the game a photorealistic quality that deepens the sense of immersion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773760/extras/BodycamGif_L.gif?t=1737116584\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Use a Specialized Remote Control</u></h2></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ll have a unique remote control that, when equipped with the right chips, enables you to open secured doors, manipulate various objects, and even engage in combat with the TV Beast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773760/extras/RemoteControlGif.gif?t=1737116584\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Variety of Monsters</u></h2></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The TV Beast can bring anything on the television screen to life\u2014whether it\u2019s psychopaths, mascots, or animals. Be ready to face an unpredictable range of threats at any moment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773760/extras/MonstersGif_L.gif?t=1737116584\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Variety of Light Sources</u></h2></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When darkness falls over the estate, make use of different light sources. Look for items like flashlights or lighters, and interact with devices such as televisions and lamps to illuminate your surroundings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773760/extras/LightSourcesGif_L.gif?t=1737116584\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Computer Usage</u></h2></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the computer in your office to browse websites, purchase essential items, eliminate threats with antivirus software, and most importantly, upgrade your remote control to better equip yourself for fighting the beast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773760/extras/UseComputerGif_L.gi